&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;    &amp;#8212;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Add retry in FileChecksumMatcher when following conditions happens:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;IOException raised from filesystem&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;No file found from output directory&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;number of files found from fs doesn&apos;t equal to expected number, which is parsed from shard name using a name template. Default template &quot;SSS-of-NNN&quot; will be used when no template is specified.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;    Default retry times are 4. Default sleep duration between each retry are 10s.&lt;/p&gt;


